testcase.name: should copy non-project properties from VersionConfig object
should return forceVersion false when project has no 'release.version' property
should return forceVersion false when project has 'release.version' property with empty value
should return forceVersion true when project has 'release.version' property with non-empty value
should return trimmed forcedVersion when project has 'release.Version' property with leading or trailing spaces
should return forceVersion true when project has deprecated 'release.forceVersion' property with non-empty value
should return ignore uncommitted changes flag from version config when no project flag present
should return ignore uncommitted changes as true when project flag present
should pick default version creator if none branch creators match
should pick version creator suitable for current branch if defined in per branch creators
should use predefined version creator when supplied with String in per branch creators
should pick default version incrementer if none branch incrementers match
should pick version incrementer suitable for current branch if defined in per branch incrementer
should use predefined incrementer creator when supplied with String in per branch incrementer
should use predefined incrementer creator with config options when supplied with String in per branch incrementer
should use incrementer passed as command line option if present
